                    "date": 1693774501702,
                    "content": "Index: \n===================================================================\n--- \n+++ \n@@ -61,9 +61,9 @@\n         <p>This loathsome demon resembles an unspeakable crossing of humanoid and fly. A chasme shuffles about on four spindly legs that can find purchase on walls and ceilings. A droning sound precedes the approach of a chasme, inflicting foes with a terrible lethargy that leaves them open to attack.</p>\r\n         <p>The lowly chasmes serve more powerful masters as interrogators or taskmasters. A chasme lives to dole out torture as punishment, and has a knack for spotting demons that have deserted their lords. Capturing and returning such traitors allows a chasme to torment the victim without fear of reprisal.</p>\r\n         <hr class=\"my-4\">\r\n         <div class=\"monsterImageContainer\">\r\n-            <img class=\"monsterPortrait\" src=\"../../../images/barlgura.webp\" alt=\"Placeholder image\">\r\n+            <img class=\"monsterPortrait\" src=\"../../../images/chasme.webp\" alt=\"Placeholder image\">\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"btn-group\" role=\"group\" aria-label=\"Basic example\">\r\n             <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" href=\"#collapseStats\" role=\"button\"\r\n                 aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapseBasic\" onclick=\"scrollToStats()\">Basic Info</button>\r\n"
